Arthur J. SNIPES et al. v. H. Wayne FRANKLIN et al. No. 7233. United States Court of Appeals Tenth Circuit. Feb. 13, 1963. George M. Murphy, Clovis, N. M., for appellants. B. C. Hernandez and Dale Walker, Albuquerque, N. M., for appellees.

Before MURRAH, Chief Judge, and BREITENSTEIN, Circuit Judge.

PER CURIAM.

On joint motion of the parties, cause remanded to the district court February 13, 1963, for purposes of entering judgment pursuant to the stipulation of the parties.
